snippet.title: Demeo Battles | Gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Let the battle commence! Demeo Battles is a competitive turn-based strategy game for 1-4 players. Choose your champion, assemble an army of monstrous minions, and team up with another champion in your quest for turn-based glory!

Wishlist now:
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1969310/Demeo_Battles/
Meta Quest - https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/4189524851131699/
